00:32:27,190 --> 00:32:29,940
Manager Chun, that wasn't me.

529
00:32:32,040 --> 00:32:34,550
Let's keep watching.

530
00:32:34,550 --> 00:32:38,490
I didn't think she had that many viewers!

531
00:32:41,150 --> 00:32:45,540
<i>Can I ask about the pattern that lady is working on?</i>

532
00:32:45,540 --> 00:32:48,489
<i>That one. A butterfly.</i>

533
00:32:48,489 --> 00:32:50,700
<i>It's so cute!</i>

534
00:32:50,700 --> 00:32:54,530
<i> I'll tie-dye a shirt to a skirt today.</i>

535
00:32:54,530 --> 00:32:58,320
A'Yao! Can you call some guys over from the warehouse to help with packing and deliveries?

536
00:32:58,320 --> 00:33:01,030
We're really busy. The boxes are running out, too.

537
00:33:01,030 --> 00:33:02,189
What about the goods?

538
00:33:02,189 --> 00:33:04,520
Some patterns are out of stock, but the rest are fine.

539
00:33:04,520 --> 00:33:05,669
Okay, I'll call people over.

540
00:33:05,669 --> 00:33:08,440
- Okay, I'll get on with my work.
- Okay!

541
00:33:26,180 --> 00:33:27,760
Hello?

542
00:33:28,620 --> 00:33:31,390
Okay, I got it. Please try to work overtime.

543
00:33:31,390 --> 00:33:32,840
Thank you.

544
00:33:32,840 --> 00:33:35,220
Brother Sen, change the tamarinds as preorders to be dispatched within a week.

545
00:33:35,220 --> 00:33:37,210
Aunty Feng, Chuchu, the tamarinds will become preorders to be dispatched within a week.

546
00:33:37,210 --> 00:33:38,840
Please explain this to the customers. Don't make mistakes.

547
00:33:38,840 --> 00:33:39,680
Okay.

548
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:42,900
Why are orders flooding in so suddenly? We can't keep up.

549
00:33:44,250 --> 00:33:46,479
Xiaoyue, call Daxia!

550
00:33:46,479 --> 00:33:48,269
We're running out of lotus seeds. Ask him if they have any.

551
00:33:48,269 --> 00:33:49,960
Okay.

552
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:51,799
We're short on manpower.

553
00:33:51,799 --> 00:33:55,080
The sudden increase in orders is keeping everyone busy.

554
00:33:55,080 --> 00:33:58,020
One of you has to come over.

555
00:33:58,020 --> 00:33:59,420
What?

556
00:33:59,420 --> 00:34:01,990
Call Xiaochun?

557
00:34:01,990 --> 00:34:05,040
Okay. I got it.

558
00:34:05,040 --> 00:34:07,049
Is there another livestream?

559
00:34:07,050 --> 00:34:08,780
It was a mess last time.

560
00:34:08,780 --> 00:34:10,200
We packed and delivered all night for days.

561
00:34:10,200 --> 00:34:11,470
After that, we received loads of returns.

562
00:34:11,470 --> 00:34:12,660
So annoying!

563
00:34:12,660 --> 00:34:14,389
Customers are just making impulse buys.

564
00:34:14,389 --> 00:34:16,579
We're slaving away because of their impulses.

565
00:34:16,579 --> 00:34:19,450
Xiaochun, come here now.

566
00:34:21,050 --> 00:34:23,690
Stop! That's too much!

567
00:34:23,690 --> 00:34:25,160
Okay.

568
00:34:25,160 --> 00:34:28,160
<i>We're at the horse ranch now.</i>

569
00:34:28,160 --> 00:34:31,909
<i>Look! The scenery is gorgeous.</i>

570
00:34:31,909 --> 00:34:36,450
<i>Handsome, can we ride outside? Along the sea.</i>

571
00:34:36,450 --> 00:34:39,729
<i>No, you can't. You can only ride on the ranch.</i>

572
00:34:39,729 --> 00:34:43,419
<i>What about the horse that the couple in the video rode by the seaside? Is that here?</i>

573
00:34:43,420 --> 00:34:45,719
<i>That horse belongs to my boss.</i>

574
00:34:45,719 --> 00:34:47,429
<i>That guy in the video is our boss.</i>

575
00:34:47,429 --> 00:34:50,349
<i>Is the lady with him his wife?</i>

576
00:34:50,349 --> 00:34:54,029
<i>Nope, she's a volunteer who was here for a vacation.</i>

577
00:34:54,029 --> 00:34:56,540
<i>She's back to run a homestay.</i>

578
00:34:56,540 --> 00:34:58,120
After making the promotional video,

579
00:34:58,120 --> 00:35:02,200
Chairman Xie and I invited many travel vloggers to come here.

580
00:35:02,200 --> 00:35:06,690
They might be able to promote it for us if they enjoyed the video.

581
00:35:06,690 --> 00:35:09,350
Look! Our hard work paid off.

582
00:35:09,350 --> 00:35:11,239
Even though this is the result,

583
00:35:11,239 --> 00:35:14,590
the process isn't what you think it will be.

584
00:35:16,320 --> 00:35:19,720
<i>I dyed this myself!</i>

585
00:35:19,720 --> 00:35:23,070
<i>This is the one you saw before. Pretty, right?</i>

586
00:35:23,070 --> 00:35:26,509
<i>I'll continue sharing stories as I open these parcels.</i>

587
00:35:26,509 --> 00:35:29,990
<i>Here's an official declaration.</i>

588
00:35:29,990 --> 00:35:34,000
<i>I swear on my love in my next life</i>

589
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:38,279
<i>[Not Sponsored]
that I didn't accept any money for this promotion.</i>

590
00:35:38,279 --> 00:35:42,069
<i>[Self-paid]
I paid for the travel vlog myself.</i>

591
00:35:42,069 --> 00:35:44,255
<i>[Fast Forward x2.0]
My fans know that I've done many travel vlogs</i>

592
00:35:44,256 --> 00:35:46,419
<i>and videos about interesting shops.</i>

593
00:35:46,420 --> 00:35:48,119
<i>We've been to so many places in China,</i>

594
00:35:48,119 --> 00:35:51,150
<i>but many places we visit can be found with a quick internet search.</i>

595
00:35:51,150 --> 00:35:53,300
<i>So, I've been wondering about uncovering new travel spots.</i>

596
00:35:53,300 --> 00:35:55,009
<i>I can bring you guys to explore and evaluate new places.</i>

597
00:35:55,010 --> 00:35:56,859
<i>As for this time,</i>

598
00:35:56,860 --> 00:36:00,300
<i>[Fan Comment]
a fan left a comment that this promotional video was amazing.</i>

599
00:36:00,300 --> 00:36:01,240
<i>They suggested that I visit.</i>

600
00:36:01,240 --> 00:36:04,239
<i>I thought it was pretty nice, so I decided to visit.</i>

601
00:36:04,239 --> 00:36:09,089
<i>[Wonderful]
To be honest, I really felt that this trip was wonderful.</i>

602
00:36:09,090 --> 00:36:11,490
<i>Even though the infrastructure there isn't well-developed,</i>

603
00:36:11,490 --> 00:36:15,939
<i>[Simple, Cozy]
the place was simple and cozy.</i>

604
00:36:15,940 --> 00:36:17,819
<i>So, I'm not lying. I only have one sentence for this.</i>

605
00:36:17,819 --> 00:36:20,650
<i>If you want to enjoy the breeze and relax,</i>

606
00:36:20,650 --> 00:36:23,440
<i>[Xie Zhiyap]
I really recommend this place.</i>

607
00:36:26,530 --> 00:36:28,870
Hello, Chairman Xie?

608
00:36:28,870 --> 00:36:31,860
Xinxin and I are watching Trekking Luo Li's video.

609
00:36:32,470 --> 00:36:34,150
I can ask her.

610
00:36:34,150 --> 00:36:35,119
Are you free?

611
00:36:35,119 --> 00:36:37,910
The tie-dye workshop is short on manpower for packing.

612
00:36:39,320 --> 00:36:41,320
Okay, we're heading over.

613
00:36:43,530 --> 00:36:44,900
Let's go.

614
00:36:45,070 --> 00:36:46,799
Where will the bookstore be?

615
00:36:46,799 --> 00:36:48,799
The village committee is allocating land for it.

616
00:36:48,799 --> 00:36:50,949
Didn't they choose Grandpa Yang's old house?

617
00:36:50,949 --> 00:36:53,730
Grandpa Yang thought that it would be noisy, so he refused.

618
00:36:53,730 --> 00:36:55,429
It's good that the village committee is allocating land.

619
00:36:55,429 --> 00:36:57,350
Everyone gets a share of the money annually.

620
00:36:57,350 --> 00:36:58,950
That's great.

621
00:36:59,600 --> 00:37:01,470
Come on, have some oranges.

622
00:37:23,260 --> 00:37:24,910
Is A'Yao here?

623
00:37:24,910 --> 00:37:26,720
He's inside.

624
00:37:30,340 --> 00:37:31,640
A'Yao.

625
00:37:32,450 --> 00:37:34,390
Uncle Deqing? Why are you here?

626
00:37:34,390 --> 00:37:37,030
I'm here about that!

627
00:37:37,030 --> 00:37:39,790
Let's speak outside.

628
00:37:39,790 --> 00:37:42,540
That? There's no rush.

629
00:37:42,540 --> 00:37:44,119
Look! We've got our hands full right now.

630
00:37:44,119 --> 00:37:47,239
Even Xiao Huang came to help out on her day off.

631
00:37:47,239 --> 00:37:50,440
Let's talk about this later.

632
00:37:50,950 --> 00:37:53,669
- Okay. I'm not in a hurry either.
- Okay.

633
00:37:53,669 --> 00:37:56,430
- I'll wait for you to contact me.
- Okay.

634
00:37:56,430 --> 00:37:58,860
Is business that booming? You're so busy.

635
00:38:11,820 --> 00:38:14,110
By the way, Uncle Deqing,

636
00:38:14,950 --> 00:38:17,070
you didn't pay the fees for using the harvester.

637
00:38:17,070 --> 00:38:18,070
Everyone else paid up.

638
00:38:18,070 --> 00:38:21,470
You can just look for the village committee's accountant.

639
00:38:21,970 --> 00:38:23,100
I totally forgot.

640
00:38:23,100 --> 00:38:25,099
- I'll go over right now.
- Okay.

641
00:38:25,099 --> 00:38:26,569
Get on with your work.

642
00:38:26,570 --> 00:38:28,190
I won't bother you.

643
00:38:47,740 --> 00:38:49,509
What allocated land?

644
00:38:49,509 --> 00:38:51,110
I don't know.

645
00:38:51,110 --> 00:38:53,070
A'Yao never talks to me about such things.

646
00:38:53,070 --> 00:38:55,260
I don't ask either.

647
00:38:55,260 --> 00:38:58,050
Everyone in the village is saying this.

648
00:38:58,050 --> 00:38:59,839
Then, it should be true.

649
00:38:59,839 --> 00:39:01,690
There are no waves without wind.

650
00:39:01,690 --> 00:39:05,509
You don't want to rent out the place anyway. This is good.

651
00:39:05,509 --> 00:39:07,900
Who said I refused to rent it out?

652
00:39:07,900 --> 00:39:10,990
A'Yao and Xiao Huang asked you time and again.

653
00:39:10,990 --> 00:39:16,339
If you were willing, why would Xiao Huang ask the village committee for land?

654
00:39:16,339 --> 00:39:18,840
Xiao Huang asked for land?

655
00:39:19,620 --> 00:39:20,989
Oh no, I spilled the beans!

656
00:39:20,989 --> 00:39:25,800
Don't tell anyone, or A'Yao will scold me again!

657
00:39:26,540 --> 00:39:29,460
Got it? I'm leaving, Aunty.

658
00:39:29,460 --> 00:39:32,040
Aunty Yang, I'll take an orange.

659
00:39:32,040 --> 00:39:33,950
Don't tell anyone!

660
00:39:33,950 --> 00:39:34,939
I won't.

661
00:39:34,940 --> 00:39:36,319
Your basket.

662
00:39:36,319 --> 00:39:37,820
Okay.

663
00:39:46,450 --> 00:39:47,570
Is that all?

664
00:39:47,570 --> 00:39:48,820
Yes.

665
00:39:48,820 --> 00:39:50,550
Thank you. We made you come over this late.

666
00:39:50,550 --> 00:39:52,470
Don't worry. More orders are good.

667
00:39:52,470 --> 00:39:54,029
What time should I come over tomorrow?

668
00:39:54,029 --> 00:39:55,429
Before 4:00 p.m.

669
00:39:55,429 --> 00:39:56,849
Okay. We'll get going.

670
00:39:56,849 --> 00:39:58,640
- Be careful.
- Okay.

671
00:40:27,190 --> 00:40:30,369
♫ <i>Do you ever feel alone</i> ♫

672
00:40:30,369 --> 00:40:33,910
♫ <i>Standing in the road</i> ♫

673
00:40:33,910 --> 00:40:36,290
Why are you hiding there?

674
00:40:36,290 --> 00:40:38,080
I'm checking whether you're slacking off.

675
00:40:38,080 --> 00:40:41,700
♫ <i>In the air, my memories flow</i> ♫

676
00:40:41,700 --> 00:40:43,610
Can't take a joke?

677
00:40:43,610 --> 00:40:46,349
♫ <i>Take a long way home</i> ♫

678
00:40:46,349 --> 00:40:50,880
What do you want for dinner? I'll cook for you.

679
00:40:50,880 --> 00:40:53,120
Tomato and egg noodles.

680
00:40:53,120 --> 00:40:57,499
Like the type made by my grandma. Fry the tomatoes and stew them into soup.

681
00:40:58,900 --> 00:41:02,100
I can't make your grandma's version.

682
00:41:02,170 --> 00:41:05,060
Want to try the husband's version?

683
00:41:05,060 --> 00:41:07,530
♫ <i>The life we can see</i> ♫

684
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:12,869
You're always so cheeky when we're alone.

685
00:41:12,869 --> 00:41:14,640
Be quiet.

686
00:41:14,640 --> 00:41:16,510
Don't remove it.

687
00:41:24,650 --> 00:41:28,870
♫ <i>It's just another day</i> ♫

688
00:41:30,700 --> 00:41:32,520
Xiaochun.

689
00:41:34,780 --> 00:41:37,570
Xiao Hu Lu is in bed,

690
00:41:37,570 --> 00:41:40,840
so I came to check if you were done.

691
00:41:42,220 --> 00:41:43,520
We're done.

692
00:41:43,520 --> 00:41:45,700
The goods have been sent out.

693
00:41:46,320 --> 00:41:48,000
We...

694
00:41:49,123 --> 00:41:50,319
We were just fooling around.

695
00:41:50,319 --> 00:41:52,670
Yes, fooling around.

696
00:41:54,910 --> 00:41:57,160
Brother,

697
00:41:57,160 --> 00:42:00,680
what's your relationship with Hongdou?

698
00:42:01,120 --> 00:42:04,520
What do you mean? I said we were fooling around.

699
00:42:06,740 --> 00:42:08,570
What?

700
00:42:08,570 --> 00:42:12,770
We're dating. Aren't we?

701
00:42:13,430 --> 00:42:14,670
Yes.

702
00:42:14,670 --> 00:42:16,200
We are.

703
00:42:16,200 --> 00:42:19,210
Brother, shame on you.

704
00:42:19,210 --> 00:42:21,099
What's so embarrassing about this?

705
00:42:21,099 --> 00:42:22,160
Ask anyone out there.

706
00:42:22,160 --> 00:42:26,010
Everyone knows you've been dying to date Hongdou for ages.

707
00:42:26,870 --> 00:42:28,760
- Cut the nonsense.
- Nonsense?

708
00:42:28,760 --> 00:42:33,970
You're the one announcing to the world that the new homestay owner is your girlfriend.

709
00:42:36,070 --> 00:42:39,340
I'm just worried that Hongdou will feel embarrassed.

710
00:42:39,340 --> 00:42:41,550
What's so embarrassing about wanting a partner?

711
00:42:41,550 --> 00:42:42,799
Everyone wants a partner, right?

712
00:42:42,799 --> 00:42:44,840
Exactly.

713
00:42:51,840 --> 00:42:56,309
Xiaochun, what about you and A'Hui?

714
00:42:57,320 --> 00:42:59,900
There's nothing between us.

715
00:42:59,900 --> 00:43:02,380
I drew the line ages ago.

716
00:43:02,380 --> 00:43:04,440
Nothing will happen.

717
00:43:05,680 --> 00:43:07,970
Isn't he pretty nice?

718
00:43:07,970 --> 00:43:09,870
You snap at him, but he never loses his temper.

719
00:43:09,870 --> 00:43:12,909
I don't like him.

720
00:43:12,909 --> 00:43:15,100
Besides, he always talks

721
00:43:15,100 --> 00:43:18,590
about the house his dad bought for him in the city.

722
00:43:18,590 --> 00:43:21,470
He's so young, but he keeps bragging about his parents' money.

723
00:43:21,470 --> 00:43:23,220
What a good-for-nothing.

724
00:43:23,220 --> 00:43:27,489
Look. He thinks a house in the city is an advantage,

725
00:43:27,489 --> 00:43:32,500
but Xie Xiaochun treats money like dirt.

726
00:43:32,500 --> 00:43:34,230
That's not right. Listen up.

727
00:43:34,230 --> 00:43:37,260
I love money.

728
00:43:37,260 --> 00:43:39,689
Bingo! Me too!

729
00:43:40,570 --> 00:43:42,769
All right. Let's get going.

730
00:43:42,769 --> 00:43:45,909
Brother, I have to tell you this.

731
00:43:45,909 --> 00:43:48,219
That old peacock is jittery.

732
00:43:48,219 --> 00:43:52,250
He confronted Xiao Huang at the village committee today.

733
00:43:52,250 --> 00:43:53,199
Did he succeed?

734
00:43:53,199 --> 00:43:54,770
Of course not.

735
00:43:54,770 --> 00:43:56,900
Who's the old peacock?

736
00:43:56,900 --> 00:43:58,099
Uncle Deqing.

737
00:43:58,099 --> 00:44:01,230
Aunty Baoping and the rest like to call him this.

738
00:44:01,870 --> 00:44:03,795
You know what, Hongdou?

739
00:44:03,796 --> 00:44:08,920
We've heard him boasting since we were young.

740
00:44:08,920 --> 00:44:13,599
He always talks about how brilliant his great-grandfather was running a business as a young man.

741
00:44:13,599 --> 00:44:16,550
All that talk about the fortunes their family made,

742
00:44:16,550 --> 00:44:17,719
the expensive food they ate, and the lavish clothes they wore.

743
00:44:17,719 --> 00:44:19,619
He was like a peacock with its feathers on display.

744
00:44:19,619 --> 00:44:21,500
Boasting whenever he could.

745
00:44:21,500 --> 00:44:22,549
I can understand that.

746
00:44:22,549 --> 00:44:26,159
I used to have a colleague named Jin in the hotel.

747
00:44:26,159 --> 00:44:28,759
His great-grandfather's first name was Aisin Gioro.

748
00:44:28,759 --> 00:44:31,159
If we were still in the Qing Dynasty,

749
00:44:31,159 --> 00:44:33,410
he would be a princess.

750
00:44:33,410 --> 00:44:35,270
Appalling.

751
00:44:35,270 --> 00:44:38,520
It's been a long day. Let's go back and rest.

752
00:44:44,130 --> 00:44:48,719
Brother, I'm worried about returned goods.

753
00:44:48,719 --> 00:44:50,009
That's out of our control.

754
00:44:50,010 --> 00:44:51,639
We have to deliver existing orders.

755
00:44:51,639 --> 00:44:55,189
- Wait a minute. Xiaochun, turn off the lights.
- Okay.

756
00:44:57,070 --> 00:44:58,680
Turn off the lights.

757
00:45:04,950 --> 00:45:06,600
Okay.

758
00:45:07,490 --> 00:45:09,130
- Let's go home.
- Come on.

